According to the law on state registration and state register of legal entities (Article 14)) the government body collects the following information:
Name of the firm; the legal address of the organization (information on the location of the permanent body, the headquarters of the governing bodies of the political party);
the organizational and legal form of the institution;
financial year; taxpayer identification number (for commercial organizations and public legal entities), registration number of a non-commercial organization; name, surname, patronymic, citizenship, and place of residence of each founder of the institution; if the founder is a legal entity, information on its name, legal address and registration if the founder is a state or municipality: name, surname, patronymic, citizenship, and place of residence of each legal representative of the institution; Information on the location, organizational and legal form and registration of the organizations established by the legal entity in the territory of the Azerbaijan Republic or outside the borders of the Azerbaijan Republic;
Information on the final decision of the court on the application of a criminal measure in the form of deprivation of the right to engage in certain activities;
information on the institution's liquidation process;
information on the prohibition of reorganization or liquidation of a legal entity by a court decision, as well as application of criminal-legal measures in the form of deprivation of a legal entity of the right to engage in certain activities;
information on the liquidation of the institution.
Few of the above points are accessible through the web service of the Tax administration. However, this is just a search tool that allows a user to search an individual legal entity and with its unique tax registration number.

Information about legal entities is available in an official form for a single case. But it is not user-friendly and does not exist as a dataset in any form.  In order to get the above-mentioned information user should know the name or taxpayer number of the company.

Through this search tool, basic company information, including company name, legal form, status, and registered address, and the name of the representer is available free of charge, in the Azerbaijani language only. And that information is mostly available not just about LLC, but about all commercial companies. Information in the search tool is timely and updated.


